snippet.title: Mini Golf Arena - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Mini Golf Arena is an exciting multiplayer mini golf game for up to 24 players online. Build & play custom maps together with your friends.

Google Play - https://mga.evolutastudio.com/mga_free_gp
Android (APK) - https://mga.evolutastudio.com/mga_apk_111
Steam - https://mga.evolutastudio.com/mga_steam
